Let's go.
But to imagine it without stronger economic, political and democratic integration, which has come into being, is another madness and a new impasse.
We need to start a new phase of European integration.
To establish a republic in France, it was necessary to "create" republicans.
A revolution of interests would not be enough.
This lesson remains in force.
We must build a Europe that is united at the economic level.
This can only be done by creating a more democratic Europe at the political level, a real people’s European sovereignty.
To create Europe, let us create Europeans.
